Port Notes:

----- version 1.0.4-1 -----
Version bump.

----- version 1.0.2-1 -----
Version bump.
Enabled backends: xlib, image, glitz, pdf, ps.

----- version 1.0.0-2 -----
Repackaged.

----- version 1.0.0-1 -----
First official release.
Enabled backends: xlib, image, and glitz.

----- version 0.9.2-1 -----
Version bump; this version should be API compatible with 1.0.
Includes support for both X11 and Win32 backends.

----- version 0.3.0-1 -----
Version bump.

----- version 0.2.0-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.


Cygwin port maintained by:
http://cygwinports.dotsrc.org/
